{"id": "1409587052781244436", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "content": "all of them are theoretically useable at e0, but horla is known to be best at e0 with e1 being a nice bonus source of weakness/vuln, and a flexible support character that can be splashed basically anywhere you need her\nhameln is the next most universal, but he operates best at e2 (arith reduction) -- still very usable & good at e0 though!!\ncorpo is probably the least-flexible out of the three, since she's very aequor/discard/tentacle dmg focused, but she's definitely top unit in that realm", "timestamp": "2025-08-25T17:15:42.244000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["126870438847578112"], "reply_to": "1409551593963261996"}
